headline: Pinnacle West: Q3 Earnings Snapshot
summary: PHOENIX (AP) — Pinnacle West Capital Corp. PNW) on Monday reported earnings of $413.2 million in its third quarter. On a per-share basis, the Phoenix-based company said it had profit of $3.39.
